					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">In performing some additional tests, I ran into another minor catch - sprite DMA actually takes 513 cycles, rather than the expected 512 (note that this does not include the 4 cycles necessary for the 'STA $4014' instruction).
<br />
<br />I have subsequently updated my emulator to reflect this information.</div>

					
